<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Doji</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles.css">
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
      }
      .card {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .hero-section {
        background: linear-gradient(120deg, #f2f2f2, #f1f1f1);
        color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
        padding: 50px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .testimonial {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    {% include "components/navbar.html.jinja" %}

    <div class="hero-section" style="black;">
      <h1>Welcome to Doji!</h1>
      <p>Your ultimate destination for fun, quality toys for kids of all ages. Start exploring today!</p>
      <a href="/browse" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-lg mt-3">Shop Now</a>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-5">
      <div class="card text-center">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h1 class="card-title">About Us</h1>
          <p class="card-text">
            At <strong>Doji</strong>, we believe in the power of play. Our mission is to bring joy and creativity to kids everywhere. We carefully curate our collection to ensure we offer only the best toys for fun, learning, and adventure.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card mt-5">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title text-center">What Do We Offer?</h2>
          <p class="card-text">
            Explore our wide range of categories designed to spark joy and creativity:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Action Figures & Dolls:</strong> Collectible characters, fun playsets, and beloved dolls from top brands.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Outdoor Toys:</strong> Everything for active play, from bikes and scooters to sports gear and outdoor games.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Arts & Crafts:</strong> Unleash creativity with craft kits, paints, markers, and DIY projects for all skill levels.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Games & Puzzles:</strong> Fun for the whole family with board games, card games, and challenging puzzles.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Stuffed Animals & Plush:</strong> Soft, cuddly companions for comfort and companionship.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Toys for All Ages:</strong> From infants to tweens, we have toys that grow with your child, making every stage special.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card mt-5">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title text-center">Featured Products</h2>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="card">
                <img src="/static/products/f1.png" class="card-img-top" alt="f1 car">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">F1 Lego Set</h5>
                  <a href="/product/1" class="btn btn-primary">View Details</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="card">
                <img src="/static/products/cybertruck-rc.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Cyberstuck remote control car">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Cyberstuck RC car</h5>
                  <a href="/product/2" class="btn btn-primary">View Details</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="card">
                <img src="/static/products/rc-drift-car.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Skymaker AE86 RC Car">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Skymaker AE86 RC Car</h5>
                  <a href="/product/3" class="btn btn-primary">View Details</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card mt-5">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title text-center">What Our Customers Say</h2>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"Doji has the best selection of toys! My kids love everything I've bought here."</p>
                <strong>- Sarah K.</strong>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"Fantastic customer service and fast delivery. Highly recommend!"</p>
                <strong>- Mike T.</strong>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"The toys are great quality, and the prices are unbeatable."</p>
                <strong>- Emma J.</strong>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"They delivered the products I ordered in 2 DAYS !!"</p>
                <strong>- Mariah Y.</strong>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"Website looks great and the products are even better!"</p>
                <strong>- Forlenza J.</strong>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"I thought these products would be some low quality products but they are actually really high quality."</p>
                <strong>- Akhter E.</strong>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="text-center mt-5 py-3">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Doji. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </body>
</html>
